long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension is designed to solve image captchas for supported websites. It retrieves the image captcha present on the page, sends the image to our server for processing, and then automatically enters the result into the input field. Currently, we only support the ve.cbi.ir, ikd.ir, iranecar.com, niopdc.ir and diplo.de website.
